[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0469","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0469.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0756","title":"Macromedia ColdFusion 管理员 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion（现 Adobe ColdFusion）管理控制台在启用高级安全功能后存在权限验证缺陷，远程未经授权的攻击者可通过 Start/Stop 管理工具直接向目标服务器发送停止操作指令，导致 ColdFusion 服务进程被异常终止，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 ColdFusion 4.x 及更早版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布安全公告并提供修复补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0756"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12","updated":"2001-03-12","remediation":"建议升级Adobe ColdFusion至2023或更高版本，并关闭Advanced Security模式或严格限制管理员账户访问权限。通过Web.config配置禁用Start/Stop实用程序功能，作为临时缓解措施可通过防火墙限制针对管理员页面的网络访问，确保仅从内部网络可访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0756.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0756","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0756.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/76af88afbb282d6c9e8ce3b9f6942bcb7e39be57/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0756.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hh79-hq4p-6w7f/GHSA-hh79-hq4p-6w7f.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0756.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--97e85f41-5b9b-4be5-b3f7-3fef80418c08.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0469.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0324","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0324.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0729","title":"Lotus Domino Server 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM Lotus Domino 服务器在处理特定网络请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于服务器程序未对输入数据长度进行充分的边界校验，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Domino 服务器发送特制的畸形数据包，使数据写入缓冲区边界之外，从而触发服务崩溃并造成拒绝服务（DoS）。该漏洞影响运行 Lotus Domino 的服务器系统，攻击无需身份认证，只要网络可达目标服务端口即可发起，利用方式相对简单，可导致邮件与协作服务中断，影响业务连续性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0729"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2001-03-12","updated":"2001-03-12","remediation":"升级至最新版本 HCL Domino 12.0.2 或更高版本以修复 Lotus Notes LDAP (NLDAP) 服务的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在 Domino 服务器配置中禁用 LDAP 服务，或通过防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问 TCP 389 端口作为临时缓解措施。同时建议定期检查服务器日志中异常的 ldap_search 请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0729.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0729","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0729.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0729.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q9vv-w9pw-fj27/GHSA-q9vv-w9pw-fj27.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0729.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0324.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0021","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0021.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0307","title":"HP HP-UX cstm 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 cstm（Customer Services Test Manager）程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖内存中的关键数据，实现权限提升并获得 root 超级用户权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，攻击者需要具有目标系统的本地访问权限，但无需其他特殊条件，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0307"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.113","remediation":"立即移除 cstm 程序的 setuid root 权限位：`chmod u-s /opt/sfm/bin/cstm`，仅允许受信任的管理员通过 sudo 执行。如业务允许，可彻底卸载 cstm 软件包：`swremove SFM-CSTM`。若系统仍在运行关键业务无法直接卸载，应使用文件权限 ACL 限制 cstm 的执行用户为 root 组，命令：`chmod 750 /opt/sfm/bin/cstm && chown root:sys /opt/sfm/bin/cstm`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0307"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0021.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1197","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1197.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1579","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9168,\"outputTokens\":27,\"totalTokens\":10859}}","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0（终端服务器版及未安装 SP6 的 NT Server 4.0）中的 Cenroll ActiveX 控件（xenroll.dll）存在拒绝服务漏洞。该控件在处理证书注册相关操作时缺乏充分资源限制，远程攻击者可在网页中嵌入恶意 ActiveX 调用，诱使用户访问后于目标主机上反复创建大量任意文件，造成磁盘空间与系统资源被耗尽，最终导致服务不可用。攻击需目标用户使用 IE 等支持 ActiveX 的浏览器访问攻击者控制的页面，无需身份认证即可触发，影响范围为未打补丁的 Windows NT 4.0 相关版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1579"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-12-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:45.793","remediation":"升级到 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6（SP6）或更高版本以修复该 ActiveX 控件缺陷；如暂无法打补丁，可在 IE 中通过「Internet 选项→安全→自定义级别」将 Cenroll (xenroll.dll) ActiveX 控件的「下载已签名的 ActiveX 控件」和「运行 ActiveX 控件」设为「禁用」或「提示」，并限制内网终端对 80/443 的可疑文件写入以缓解拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3B242366","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/3062","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/6827","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7107","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-1579.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1579.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1579","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1579.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1579.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8p3f-96gj-gwpg/GHSA-8p3f-96gj-gwpg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1579.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--cc335ba8-6c1b-4caa-9751-e38b9f7f14a0.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1197.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0477","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0477.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0761","title":"FreeBSD fts 库缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统 fts 库例程存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过精心构造的数据触发该漏洞，导致内存越界写入。该漏洞允许攻击者利用 periodic 程序修改任意系统文件，从而提升权限至 root 级别。漏洞影响 FreeBSD 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地账户权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0761"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.190","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 3.3 及以上版本，该版本修复了 fts 库函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，限制本地用户对 periodic 程序的执行权限，移除不必要的 cron 任务调用。同时应用系统安全补丁集，确保所有基础库为最新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1074","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/644"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0477.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0576","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0576.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0812","title":"Samba smbmnt 竞争条件导致本地用户挂载任意文件系统漏洞","description":"Samba smbmnt 组件存在竞争条件漏洞，本地攻击者可利用 smbmnt 挂载文件系统时的竞争窗口，通过精心构造的时序攻击将文件系统挂载到任意指定位置，从而实现权限提升或文件系统劫持。该漏洞影响运行 Samba smbmnt 组件的 Linux/Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地用户权限并能调用 smbmnt 命令，利用竞争窗口在挂载操作完成前替换挂载点路径，实现任意路径挂载从而实现权限提升或敏感文件访问。CVSS 评分 7.6，属高危漏洞，建议升级 Samba 至修复版本并限制 smbmnt 执行权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0812"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-07-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.467","remediation":"建议升级 Samba 至 2.0.7 或更高版本（1999 年 9 月发布的修复版本）。若无法立即升级，可移除 smbmnt 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/smbmnt）或限制普通用户执行权限（chmod 750 /usr/bin/smbmnt），并限制普通用户挂载权限（编辑 /etc/fstab 添加 user,noauto 选项或使用 sudo 限制）作为临时缓解措施。建议尽快升级至 Samba 4.x 以上长期支持版本彻底修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0812","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0812.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0812","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0812.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0812.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qh4j-xq27-qw86/GHSA-qh4j-xq27-qw86.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0812.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152600_152700.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990804.data","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2021/samba/gb_samba_mult_vuln_2_0_5.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0812.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0576.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0855","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1008","title":"Red Hat xsoldier 0.96 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xsoldier 0.96 是 RedHat Linux 6.2 发行版中附带的 X11 窗口射击游戏，该程序在启动时未对命令行参数长度进行充分边界检查，存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向 xsoldier 传入超长命令行参数触发堆栈溢出，进而覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，最终获得系统 root 权限。此漏洞影响 RedHat 6.2 系统上安装 xsoldier 0.96 版本的本地用户，攻击条件要求攻击者已在目标系统上拥有普通用户账户访问权限，利用方式为在命令行中执行带有精心构造的溢出载荷的参数即可完成权限提升。CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级为高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1008"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"2000-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:30.753","remediation":"卸载 xsoldier 0.96 游戏或移除其 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/X11R6/bin/xsoldier），建议升级至 Red Hat 7.0 或更高版本，或从红帽官方获取 xsoldier 修补版本进行升级。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1008","http://marc.info/?l=freebsd-security&m=94531826621620&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/871","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/229"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/229"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/229"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0855.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0084","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0427","title":"Qualcomm Eudora 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qualcomm Eudora 邮件客户端（包括 Eudora 4.1/4.2/4.3、Eudora Light 3.0、Eudora Pro 1.0）在处理附件时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送带有超长文件名的恶意邮件附件触发该漏洞，导致邮件客户端崩溃或拒绝服务。由于对附件文件名字段长度缺乏有效校验，攻击者可构造特制邮件批量发送，使目标用户无法正常使用邮件客户端。该漏洞 CVSS v2 评分 7.5，危害等级高，且可能伴随部分机密性和完整性影响。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0427"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-05-01","updated":"2000-05-01","remediation":"升级至 Eudora 5.0 或更高版本（5.x/6.x 系列已修复此漏洞），并避免打开来源不明的包含超长附件名的邮件。由于 Eudora 已于 2006 年停止维护，建议迁移至 Thunderbird 等仍在安全更新的邮件客户端以防止后续安全风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0427.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0427","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0427.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c