方式是攻击者读取该安装文件即可获取 Administrator 密码，进而以最高权限登录并完全控制系统，造成严重的权限泄露与安全隐患。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0701"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-04-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.677","remediation":"微软已在 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 及后续补丁中修复该问题，应立即升级至 SP4 或更高版本；完成无人参与安装后，手动删除分布于磁盘的 Unattend.txt、Winnt.sif 等应答文件，避免其中包含的本地 Administrator 密码等敏感信息泄露；同时在共享与权限配置中禁止对系统分区及 %SystemRoot% 目录的匿名访问，并定期审计已部署镜像中的安装残留文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ173039","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/626","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-036","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8b4df384387a55d60e5ec37568fb4254388bef40/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0701","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0701.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/30f77465b94d71209b45a239e791a1fe062c9e8b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/c9462134bd15c86fd0ed45fb18bd761cdf938c73/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-26w9-58jr-4jc3/GHSA-26w9-58jr-4jc3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0701.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ce201f9a-05b7-4813-a26f-ecc530d4b35a.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001276.txt","https://github.com/chandanbn/notes/blob/90eb64532f7259c55e5531dfc2726d810d17ef6e/cve5-validation-errors-Jan27.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0280.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0280.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0274","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0274.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0699","title":"Bluestone Sapphire Web Server 会话劫持漏洞","description":"Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器存在会话劫持漏洞，其会话 ID 生成算法过于简单且可预测，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过枚举或猜测会话 ID 的方式劫持合法用户的会话，从而获取未授权访问权限。该漏洞影响 Bluestone Sapphire Web 服务器的多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议升级至修复版本或实施会话加固措施。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0699"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-04-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.427","remediation":"升级 Bluestone Sapphire Web Server 至最新版本或迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）。在无法升级时，在应用层实施强随机 Session ID 生成机制，并启用 HTTPS 加密传输防止会话劫持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/623","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8b4df384387a55d60e5ec37568fb4254388bef40/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0699.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0699","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0699.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/30f77465b94d71209b45a239e791a1fe062c9e8b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0699.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/849e6f9df06cb942837b4a38ccc3fd5e713aabe0/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rq8-xfj6-8rw6/GHSA-9rq8-xfj6-8rw6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0699.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/76bb1d23d06b407ea0a69eb647ae84de20da916f/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0274.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0274.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0264","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0264.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0695","title":"Sybase PowerDynamo 路径穿越任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Sybase PowerDynamo 个人 Web 服务器存在路径遍历漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 URL 中的 ../ 序列绕过访问限制，远程读取服务器文件系统上的任意文件（如 /etc/passwd 等敏感文件），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响系统机密性，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0695"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Sybase PowerDynamo 已停止维护，建议立即迁移至 SAP 官方推荐的替代产品（如 SAP ASE Web 服务或迁移至现代 Web 服务器）。如无法迁移，在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 重写规则拦截包含 .. 的请求路径，并限制 Web 服务进程对系统敏感文件的读取权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1064","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/620"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0264.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0525","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0790","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16272,\"outputTokens\":34,\"totalTokens\":16306}}","description":"Netscape 浏览器存在缓存信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在网页中嵌入恶意 JavaScript 代码，利用浏览器同源策略的不足读取目标用户缓存中的敏感数据。由于 Netscape 浏览器（ Communicator 系列）的缓存机制缺乏对 JavaScript 访问的适当限制，攻击者可在用户不知情的情况下，通过构造特定脚本触发缓存查询并获取信息。该漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 等版本，攻击条件要求用户在浏览恶意页面时目标缓存中存在相关数据，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。Netscape 官方已发布安全公告建议用户升级至修复版本。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0790"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.810","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.5 或更高版本以修复此漏洞，Netscape 官方已在安全公告中提供补丁。如无法立即升级，可在浏览器安全设置中禁用 JavaScript 作为临时缓解措施，阻止恶意脚本访问缓存数据。建议优先通过 Netscape 官网获取最新安全版本，并清除现有浏览器缓存以防止已缓存的敏感信息被读取。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://home.netscape.com/security/notes/jscachebrowsing.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2d7ee098b36909e6f1960d9a77b8043812c482f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0790.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0790","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0790.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0790.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mvw7-68fw-g45r/GHSA-mvw7-68fw-g45r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0790.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--55a0b034-c223-4289-b30c-2a9571d15929.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/47100ba13b280d8b2c20065cb4252225c6015d54/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--55a0b034-c223-4289-b30c-2a9571d15929.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0525.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0262","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0262.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0693","title":"Digital UNIX、AIX、CDE、IRIX、Solaris、SunOS ToolTalk 共享库 TT_SESSION 环境变量本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"tags.<value>ToolTalk 共享库在处理 TT_SESSION 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过精心构造该环境变量的内容，触发堆栈缓冲区溢出，进而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响多个 Unix 系统版本，包括 DIGITAL UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、CDE 2.1、IRIX 6.5.14、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4。成功利用该漏洞后，本地低权限用户可获得 root 权限，完全控制系统。攻击条件为攻击者已拥有目标系统的本地访问权限。CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0693"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2000-03-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.690","remediation":"建议立即安装各厂商针对此漏洞发布的安全补丁：Solaris 应用 Sun 的 ToolTalk 补丁（如 105396 系列），IRIX 升级至 6.5.15 或应用 SGI 的补丁，AIX 安装 APAR 修复并升级至 4.3.3，DIGITAL UNIX 应用 OSF/1 补丁集。在无法立即打补丁前，可通过删除或限制 /usr/dt/lib/libtt* 共享库及 setuid 程序的写执行权限、对普通用户移除 CDE/ToolTalk 相关 setuid 二进制文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/641","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A4374","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19501","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2e66cc19cc703324c2947fd6e7687a8b094f9fa/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0693","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0693.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0f6f0e28732bc614273e91613aef04def1dce90b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0693.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/c137f5e2e6bb5d0d49e919ecf3efde0b10d9a781/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj/GHSA-wjxh-cxm3-22mj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee1